'''LIN Corporation''' was a company located on the planet [[Aleron]] and was the maker of the [[LIN demolitionmech autonomous minelayer/Legends|LIN demolitionmech autonomous minelayers]].<ref name="LE">''[[Lords of the Expanse]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
''[[Galaxy Guide 7: Mos Eisley]]'' and ''[[The Essential Guide to Droids]]'' identifies [[Cybot Galactica/Legends|Cybot Galactica]] as the LIN-series droids' as their manufacturer.<ref name="LE" />

